<Link id="l00334" /><CodeLine lineNumber="334"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// by S&#95;DEFRANGE&#95;FRAMEPOINTER&#95;REL records to find local variables.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00336" /><CodeLine lineNumber="336"><Highlight kind="normal">      FuncOS &lt;&lt; </Highlight><Highlight kind="stringliteral">&quot;$T0 &quot;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &lt;&lt; CFAVar &lt;&lt; </Highlight><Highlight kind="charliteral">&#39; &#39;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> &lt;&lt; <a href="/docs/api/structs/anonymous-namespace-x86wincofftargetstreamer-cpp-/fpostatemachine/#a604b633d7149d5e7990a3ab9e0d73867">StackOffsetBeforeAlign</a> &lt;&lt; </Highlight><Highlight kind="stringliteral">&quot; - &quot;</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00340" /><CodeLine lineNumber="340"><Highlight kind="normal">    </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// The address of return address is ESP + CurOffset, but we use .raSearch to</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
